@node Main "SafeKraker - Documentation"

                            'SafeKraker' 1.05

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'SafeKraker' is a code-breaking type of @{" game " link play}, where you try to
find the secret 3-number combination in the least amount of moves.

  The numbers in each column range from 1 to 7, there is a padlock
icon on top of each column that opens when you have found the right
number for that column.

  You @{" play " link play} by clicking on the arrows which will increase or
decrease the numbers in their respective columns (an arrow
pointing up will increase the number and the arrow pointing
down will decrease it).

  Have fun!

